      "description": "Predicted hemolysis index values were compared against published hemolysis data drawn from peer-reviewed literature covering similar centrifugal pump geometries. The literature sources were treated as surrogate benchmarks, and agreement within reported scatter bands was taken as confirmation of model adequacy. No dedicated experimental campaign was conducted; the assessment team judged published data sufficient to bound prediction uncertainty.",
