        "name": "Systematic literature review of hemolysis index benchmarks",
        "description": "A structured search of peer-reviewed publications (2010–2024) was performed to identify reported hemolysis index measurements for centrifugal blood pumps operating in the VAD flow-speed envelope. Fourteen studies were identified; mean and standard deviation of reported NIH values were extracted and compared to CFD predictions. No new physical experiments were performed."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/validation/cou2-uncertainty-quantification-result",
