      "name": "Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification on hemolysis predictions",
      "description": "Monte Carlo sampling over inlet boundary condition uncertainties and fluid viscosity variability was performed across 5 flow-speed operating points. 95th-percentile hemolysis index predictions remained below the clinical acceptance threshold in all cases.",
